{"name":"毕设","postlist":[{"title":"python_django","slug":"python-django","date":"2021-11-02T14:19:14.000Z","updated":"2021-12-08T12:26:40.812Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/python-django.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"https://i.loli.net/2020/05/01/gkihqEjXxJ5UZ1C.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"我的笔记\"><a href=\"#我的笔记\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我的笔记\"></a>我的笔记</h1><p><a href=\"https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3/library/venv.html\">官方文档</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">平台</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Shell</th>\n<th align=\"left\">用于激活虚拟环境的命令</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"left\">POSIX</td>\n<td align=\"left\">bash/zsh</td>\n<td align=\"left\">$ source <venv>/bin/activate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n<td align=\"left\">fish</td>\n<td align=\"left\">$ source <venv>/bin/activate.fish</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n<td align=\"left\">csh/tcsh</td>\n<td align=\"left\">$ source <venv>/bin/activate.csh</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n<td align=\"left\">PowerShell Core</td>\n<td align=\"left\">$ <venv>/bin/Activate.ps1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">Windows</td>\n<td align=\"left\">cmd.exe</td>\n<td align=\"left\">C:&gt; <venv>\\Scripts\\activate.bat</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n<td align=\"left\">PowerShell</td>\n<td align=\"left\">PS C:&gt; <venv>\\Scripts\\Activate.ps1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>创建网站框架</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">.\\django-admin.exe startproject mysite</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>启动django框架</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python manage.py runserver</span><br><span class=\"line\">python manage.py runserver [端口号]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>网站中的一个功能创建应用</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python .\\manage.py startapp index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>数据库迁移</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python manage.py migate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>列出django子命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python manage .py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h1 id=\"目录解读\"><a href=\"#目录解读\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"目录解读\"></a>目录解读</h1><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129095301686.png\" alt=\"image-20211129095301686\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129104235294.png\" alt=\"image-20211129104235294\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129104304785.png\" alt=\"image-20211129104304785\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129104323422.png\" alt=\"image-20211129104323422\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129104800457.png\" alt=\"image-20211129104800457\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129104820337.png\" alt=\"image-20211129104820337\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129104940840.png\" alt=\"image-20211129104940840\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129105214895.png\" alt=\"image-20211129105214895\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129105351007.png\" alt=\"image-20211129105351007\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129105747983.png\" alt=\"image-20211129105747983\"></p>\n<p>我的理解</p>\n<p>目前在我看来视图（view）就是用来写html的文件，urls就是将这个文件的路径导入，使得可以在浏览器显示</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129110849895.png\" alt=\"image-20211129110849895\"></p>\n<p>浏览器访问page/2003/    djgano匹配到视图（views）中有page_2003中有函数，然后输出函数的内容</p>\n<p>这是路由吗？？我感觉是，因为urls将浏览器请求的url地址指向views</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129111001293.png\" alt=\"image-20211129111001293\"><img src=\"/images/image-20211129111029113.png\" alt=\"image-20211129111029113\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"路由配置\"><a href=\"#路由配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"路由配置\"></a>路由配置</h1><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129111214428.png\" alt=\"image-20211129111214428\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"路由配置-path\"><a href=\"#路由配置-path\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"路由配置 - path\"></a>路由配置 - path</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129111418584.png\" alt=\"image-20211129111418584\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"路由配置-path-转换器\"><a href=\"#路由配置-path-转换器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"路由配置 - path - 转换器\"></a>路由配置 - path - 转换器</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129112600885.png\" alt=\"image-20211129112600885\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"路由配置-path-转换器-1\"><a href=\"#路由配置-path-转换器-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"路由配置 - path - 转换器\"></a>路由配置 - path - 转换器</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129112814502.png\" alt=\"image-20211129112814502\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"测试\"><a href=\"#测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试\"></a>测试</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129113915653.png\" alt=\"image-20211129113915653\"><img src=\"/images/image-20211129113939729.png\" alt=\"image-20211129113939729\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129113926093.png\" alt=\"image-20211129113926093\"><img src=\"/images/image-20211129114053987.png\" alt=\"image-20211129114053987\"></p>\n<p>可以看出来，执行的时候是由上而下执行</p>\n<h3 id=\"练习：计算器\"><a href=\"#练习：计算器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"练习：计算器\"></a>练习：计算器</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129123645517.png\" alt=\"image-20211129123645517\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"路由配置-re-path\"><a href=\"#路由配置-re-path\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"路由配置 - re_path()\"></a>路由配置 - re_path()</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129141056822.png\" alt=\"image-20211129141056822\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"样例\"><a href=\"#样例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例\"></a>样例</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129141712298.png\" alt=\"image-20211129141712298\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"生日正则：\"><a href=\"#生日正则：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生日正则：\"></a>生日正则：</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129145314266.png\" alt=\"image-20211129145314266\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129145335743.png\" alt=\"image-20211129145335743\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129145352623.png\" alt=\"image-20211129145352623\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"Django中的请求\"><a href=\"#Django中的请求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Django中的请求\"></a>Django中的请求</h1><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129170039257.png\" alt=\"image-20211129170039257\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129171430226.png\" alt=\"image-20211129171430226\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Django中的响应对象\"><a href=\"#Django中的响应对象\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Django中的响应对象\"></a>Django中的响应对象</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129172858756.png\" alt=\"image-20211129172858756\"></p>\n<p>Django中的响应对象</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129173135044.png\" alt=\"image-20211129173135044\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129173257111.png\" alt=\"image-20211129173257111\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"GET处理\"><a href=\"#GET处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"GET处理\"></a>GET处理</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129174221824.png\" alt=\"image-20211129174221824\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129174751910.png\" alt=\"image-20211129174751910\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129175033023.png\" alt=\"image-20211129175033023\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"POST处理\"><a href=\"#POST处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"POST处理\"></a>POST处理</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129201247287.png\" alt=\"image-20211129201247287\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129201306505.png\" alt=\"image-20211129201306505\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129201327000.png\" alt=\"image-20211129201327000\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"传统的mvc\"><a href=\"#传统的mvc\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"传统的mvc\"></a>传统的mvc</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211129203627800.png\" alt=\"image-20211129203627800\"></p>\n<p>Django是MTV结构</p>\n<h1 id=\"模板配置\"><a href=\"#模板配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板配置\"></a>模板配置</h1><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211130185916088.png\" alt=\"image-20211130185916088\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"模板加载方式\"><a href=\"#模板加载方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板加载方式\"></a>模板加载方式</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211130190516341.png\" alt=\"image-20211130190516341\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211130191454722.png\" alt=\"image-20211130191454722\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"视图层与模板层之间的交互\"><a href=\"#视图层与模板层之间的交互\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"视图层与模板层之间的交互\"></a>视图层与模板层之间的交互</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211130192009564.png\" alt=\"image-20211130192009564\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"例子：\"><a href=\"#例子：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"例子：\"></a>例子：</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201150602148.png\" alt=\"image-20211201150602148\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201150617963.png\" alt=\"image-20211201150617963\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"模板的变量\"><a href=\"#模板的变量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板的变量\"></a>模板的变量</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201151027473.png\" alt=\"image-20211201151027473\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"调用方法\"><a href=\"#调用方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"调用方法\"></a>调用方法</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201151055547.png\" alt=\"image-20211201151055547\"></p>\n<p>都是用双大括号加变量名</p>\n<p>测试各种变量的传值</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201152336107.png\" alt=\"image-20211201152336107\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201152350065.png\" alt=\"image-20211201152350065\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201152402659.png\" alt=\"image-20211201152402659\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"模板标签\"><a href=\"#模板标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板标签\"></a>模板标签</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201152701477.png\" alt=\"image-20211201152701477\"></p>\n<p>基本都需要结束标签，个别特殊的不需要结束标签，</p>\n<h3 id=\"if标签\"><a href=\"#if标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if标签\"></a>if标签</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201153028048.png\" alt=\"image-20211201153028048\"></p>\n<p><code>if</code>标签的结束标签是<code>endif</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201153132882.png\" alt=\"image-20211201153132882\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"测试例子\"><a href=\"#测试例子\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试例子\"></a>测试例子</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211201153747378.png\" alt=\"image-20211201153747378\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211203101238114.png\" alt=\"image-20211203101238114\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211203101258139.png\" alt=\"image-20211203101258139\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"for标签\"><a href=\"#for标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"for标签\"></a>for标签</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211204160943943.png\" alt=\"image-20211204160943943\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"模板过滤器\"><a href=\"#模板过滤器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板过滤器\"></a>模板过滤器</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211204162513617.png\" alt=\"image-20211204162513617\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"常用过滤器\"><a href=\"#常用过滤器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用过滤器\"></a>常用过滤器</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211204162620250.png\" alt=\"image-20211204162620250\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"模板继承\"><a href=\"#模板继承\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板继承\"></a>模板继承</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211204164816564.png\" alt=\"image-20211204164816564\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"父页面传入的参数无法继承给子页面\"><a href=\"#父页面传入的参数无法继承给子页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"父页面传入的参数无法继承给子页面\"></a>父页面传入的参数无法继承给子页面</h3><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211204185525663.png\" alt=\"image-20211204185525663\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"url书写规范\"><a href=\"#url书写规范\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"url书写规范\"></a>url书写规范</h1><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211207203612783.png\" alt=\"image-20211207203612783\"></p>\n<p><code>相对地址使用较多</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211207203845679.png\" alt=\"image-20211207203845679\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"url反向解析\"><a href=\"#url反向解析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"url反向解析\"></a>url反向解析</h2><p><img src=\"/images/image-20211208153642369.png\" alt=\"image-20211208153642369\"></p>\n<p>代码：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">html</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;&#123;% url &#x27;tr&#x27; &#x27;100&#x27; %&#125;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>url反向解析版本<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">路由配置</span><br><span class=\"line\">path(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;test_urls_result/&lt;int:age&gt;&#x27;</span>, views.test_url_result, name=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;tr&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">视图配置</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">test_url_result</span>(<span class=\"params\">request, age</span>):</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> HttpResponse(<span class=\"string\">&quot;---test_url_result is ok----&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>优点：可以动态获取url，因为是通过别名来</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"python","path":"api/categories/python.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"毕设","path":"api/tags/毕设.json"},{"name":"自学","path":"api/tags/自学.json"}]}]}